{{vgname|雷盖亚 决斗传奇|ja=レガイア デュエルサーガ，Legaia Duel Saga|en=Legaia 2: Duel Saga|diff=yes|cn=雷盖亚 决斗传奇|tw=異世界傳說2|中国大陆也常称“'''雷蓋亞傳說2'''”}}，是由Porkion开发的[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]][[电子角色扮演游戏|角色扮演游戏]]<ref name="developer interview">{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamezone.com/news/gz_interview_prokion_s_president_talks_about_the_innovations_brought_to_the_legaia_continent_in_legaia_2_duel_saga |title=GZ Interview: Prokions president talks about the innovations brought to the Legaia continent in Legaia 2 Duel Saga |accessdate=2014-09-01 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303221729/http://www.gamezone.com/news/gz_interview_prokion_s_president_talks_about_the_innovations_brought_to_the_legaia_continent_in_legaia_2_duel_saga |dead-url=no }}</ref>，为1998年游戏《[[雷盖亚传说|雷盖亚传说]]》的续作。游戏于2001年在日本由[[索尼电脑娱乐|索尼电脑娱乐]]发行，次年由[[Eidos_Interactive|Eidos Interactive]]在北美和欧洲发行。

== 评价 ==

《雷盖亚 决斗传奇》在日本杂志《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》的得分为28/40<ref>{{cite journal| journal=ファミ通 | issue=677 | title=クロスレビュー | year=2001 | language=ja}}</ref>。游戏在西方反响一般，在[[Game_Rankings|Game Rankings]]和[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]的汇总得分为70%和67<ref name="GR">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/ps2/520833-legaia-2-duel-saga/index.html|title=Legaia 2: Duel Saga|publisher=[[Game_Rankings|Game Rankings]]|accessdate=2011-10-24|archive-date=2011-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111121231145/http://www.gamerankings.com/ps2/520833-legaia-2-duel-saga/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="MC">{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-2/legaia-2-duel-saga|title=Legaia 2: Duel Saga|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2011-10-24|archive-date=2012-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120302231338/http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-2/legaia-2-duel-saga|dead-url=no}}</ref>，没有前作成功。

《Fami通》的销量统计显示，游戏首周在日本销量为40,302套，在当周全部新发售游戏中排名第6。游戏以53,808套的銷量勉強登上[[電擊Online|電擊Online]]的2001年度暢銷遊戲Top 200<ref>{{cite web | author=IGN staff | date=January 11, 2002 | title=Dengeki Online Top 200 Of 2001 | url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/100/100860p1.html | publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] | accessdate=May 2, 2012 | archive-date=2011-06-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629133446/http://ps2.ign.com/articles/100/100860p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

